title: Undertow-1996-Lou Diamond Phillips
description:
Movie Description
In this thriller from the Showtime cable network a stranded young man is terrorized by a menacing mountain man whose beautiful wife gets caught in the middle.

Credits 
Cast: Lou Diamond Phillips 
Director: Eric Red, Fred Weintraub, Tom Kuhn 
Producer: David M. Perlmutter, Lewis B. Chesler 

Synopsis
A traveling salesman gets caught in a bizarre triangle when he encounters a wild mountain-man and his desperate, beautiful young wife.
